Lexical Vars:

Loading DynLexPad (thanks to mdiep telling me about languages/tcl/src/tclsh.pir example):
.sub _load_lib :immediate
    .local pmc lib     
    lib = loadlib 'dynlexpad'
.end               
            
.HLL 'Python', 'python_group'
.HLL_map .LexPad, .DynLexPad

Or just link it into group add HLL Python map LexPad
